label: [{"start":0,"end":10,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":22,"text":"免疫抑制性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":32,"text":"反转录病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"禽类","labels":["type"]},{"start":55,"end":65,"text":"急性致死性网状细胞瘤","labels":["disease"]},{"start":91,"end":95,"text":"禽用疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":82,"end":86,"text":"慢性肿瘤","labels":["disease"]},{"start":50,"end":54,"text":"免疫抑制","labels":["disease"]},{"start":66,"end":71,"text":"矮小综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":72,"end":76,"text":"淋巴组织","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 禽网状内皮组织增生病是一种新的免疫抑制性疾病，是由一组反转录病毒引起禽类的一组症状不同的综合征，包括免疫抑制、急性致死性网状细胞瘤，矮小综合征和淋巴组织及其他组织的慢性肿瘤，它是污染禽用疫苗的潜在因素。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":16,"text":"免疫应答能力降低","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"抗病力下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":23,"end":33,"text":"干扰其他疫苗免疫效应","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 家禽感染后，造成免疫应答能力降低，抗病力下降，干扰其他疫苗免疫效应，导致免疫失败。

label: [{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"鸡痘","labels":["disease"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"球虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":29,"end":34,"text":"沙门氏菌病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 它又可潜在地引起病毒突变并易激发感染鸡痘、支气管炎、球虫、沙门氏菌病等，造成巨大经济损失。

label: [{"start":7,"end":18,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"乙醚","labels":["drug"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"氯仿","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 1.病原特性：禽网状内皮组织增生病毒对理化因素抵抗力不强，容易被乙醚、氯仿杀灭，对热敏感，不耐酸，耐低温。

label: [{"start":9,"end":19,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":43,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":44,"end":47,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":58,"end":68,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 2.流行病学特征：禽网状内皮组织增生病可垂直传播，也可水平传播，其水平传播主要经呼吸道和消化道感染，污染疫苗的传播是禽网状内皮组织增生病发生的重要因素。

label: [{"start":15,"end":22,"text":"急性网状细胞瘤","labels":["disease"]},{"start":42,"end":46,"text":"急性死亡","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 3.临床症状与病理变化：(1)急性网状细胞瘤发病急，很少见到临床症状，多于1～2天内急性死亡，死亡率可达100%。

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"脾肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"脾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":27,"text":"小点状或弥漫性灰白色病灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":33,"text":"肾脏也肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":50,"text":"卵巢出现纤维性粘连","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":50,"text":"纤维性粘连","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"胰腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":40,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 剖检见肝、脾肿大，表面及切面有小点状或弥漫性灰白色病灶；肾脏也肿胀，胰腺、输卵管及卵巢出现纤维性粘连。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"矮小综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"生长发育迟缓","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"体形瘦小","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"参差不齐","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":36,"text":"饲料消耗不减","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"血液稀薄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"稀薄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"贫血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"全身出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":57,"text":"腺胃充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":58,"end":60,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":64,"end":68,"text":"黏膜糜烂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":66,"end":68,"text":"糜烂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"溃疡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"血液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":64,"end":66,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)矮小综合征：生长发育迟缓或停滞、体形瘦小，参差不齐，但饲料消耗不减，剖检见血液稀薄，贫血，全身出血；腺胃充血、出血、肿胀，黏膜糜烂或溃疡；

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"脾脏坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"法氏囊萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":26,"text":"臂神经肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":38,"text":"横纹消失呈黄白或灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":38,"text":"灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"黄白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":46,"text":"水肿样明显增粗","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":54,"end":68,"text":"卵巢有时也见弥漫性灰白色病灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":66,"end":68,"text":"病灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":66,"text":"灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"脾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"胸腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"法氏囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"坐骨神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"臂神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"胰腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":50,"end":51,"text":"心","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":52,"end":53,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":54,"end":56,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 脾脏坏死，胸腺及法氏囊萎缩；两侧坐骨神经、臂神经肿胀，横纹消失呈黄白或灰白色，水肿样明显增粗；胰腺、心、肾及卵巢有时也见弥漫性灰白色病灶。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"慢性淋巴瘤","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"精神委顿","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"食欲不振","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":27,"text":"淋巴样白血病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":37,"end":41,"text":"肿瘤病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":29,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"胸腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"心脏","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (3)慢性淋巴瘤：精神委顿，食欲不振，产生淋巴样白血病，肝、胸腺、心脏均有肿瘤病变。

label: [{"start":0,"end":10,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"肝脾肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"点状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":30,"text":"弥漫性灰白色病灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":39,"text":"法氏囊萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":46,"text":"生长发育障碍","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":51,"text":"个体瘦小","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":52,"end":59,"text":"饲料消耗不减少","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"肝脾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"胸腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"法氏囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 禽网状内皮组织增生病特点是肝脾肿大，有点状或弥漫性灰白色病灶；胸腺、法氏囊萎缩，生长发育障碍，个体瘦小，饲料消耗不减少；

label: [{"start":1,"end":3,"text":"肿瘤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"肢体麻痹","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"麻痹","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肢体","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"肿瘤性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":46,"end":54,"text":"马立克氏病神经型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":57,"end":63,"text":"一侧神经肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":64,"end":68,"text":"横纹消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":70,"end":80,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":81,"end":89,"text":"两侧神经同时病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":87,"end":89,"text":"病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":59,"end":61,"text":"神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":83,"end":85,"text":"神经","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有肿瘤或肢体麻痹。但这些特征与其他肿瘤性疾病有很多相似处，所以难以鉴别，然而仍有不同之处，如马立克氏病神经型表现为一侧神经肿胀，横纹消失，而禽网状内皮组织增生病为两侧神经同时病变；

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"内脏型马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"肿瘤病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"内脏器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"皮肤型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"眼型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":31,"end":41,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":50,"end":52,"text":"肿瘤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":44,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":45,"end":46,"text":"脾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":48,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 内脏型马立克氏病除内脏器官的肿瘤病变之外，还有皮肤型、眼型，而禽网状内皮组织增生病仅有肝、脾或肾出现肿瘤。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"白血病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"外周神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"心脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"神经症状","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 再如白血病不出现神经症状，没有外周神经的病理变化，心脏病变也不明显。真正做到确实可靠的诊断，应做病毒分离和抗体监测加以证实。

label: [{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"商品疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":23,"end":33,"text":"禽网状内皮组织增生病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"种鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":49,"end":52,"text":"阳性鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":55,"end":58,"text":"种鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":37,"end":46,"text":"及时监测种鸡群抗体","labels":["control"]},{"start":47,"end":52,"text":"淘汰阳性鸡","labels":["control"]},{"start":53,"end":58,"text":"净化种鸡群","labels":["control"]},{"start":59,"end":71,"text":"禁止发病鸡场种蛋进入市场","labels":["control"]}]
text: 目前尚无商品疫苗，亦无有效治疗方法，主要是预防禽网状内皮组织增生病的发生，及时监测种鸡群抗体，淘汰阳性鸡，净化种鸡群，禁止发病鸡场种蛋进入市场，杜绝垂直传播的机会；

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"感染鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":0,"end":10,"text":"发现感染鸡群迅速隔离","labels":["control"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"病鸡淘汰","labels":["control"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":23,"end":32,"text":"感染鸡舍要彻底清洗","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]}]
text: 发现感染鸡群迅速隔离，病鸡淘汰、捕杀、烧毁；对感染鸡舍要彻底清洗、消毒，防止水平传播。
